---
source: crates/daemon/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
List contacts where the most recent inbound is older than the outbound by more than --threshold-days days. Surfaces "going cold" relationships

Usage: mxr contacts decay [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --threshold-days <THRESHOLD_DAYS>
          [default: 30]
      --max-lookback-days <MAX_LOOKBACK_DAYS>
          Upper bound: ignore contacts whose last inbound is older than this. Default ~3 years keeps focus on relationships you might still rebuild; raise for a wider audit [default: 1095]
      --limit <LIMIT>
          [default: 50]
      --account <ACCOUNT>

  -h, --help
          Print help
